data.description: Welcome home to 8221 Pickop Miles Court! This beautiful home is nestled on a large corner lot and boasts 4-bedrooms and 2.5-bathrooms! As you arrive you will love the warm and welcome curb appeal from the well manicured lawn to the front porch! Amazing location and within minutes of Boeing, Charleston International Airport, Tanger Outlets where you can enjoy shopping, dining and so much more! The versatile an open floor plan creates the ease of entertaining family and friends! The fully fenced in backyard is very spacious and private! The home will be open for showings Saturday 1/6 11-2PM!
